&lt;p&gt;In an effort to keep things organized, I&amp;rsquo;ve laid out this post for your stank ass.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&#34;front-matter-considerations&#34;&gt;Front Matter Considerations&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When filling in the &lt;code&gt;author&lt;/code&gt; attribute, use your full name &lt;code&gt;Michael Peritore&lt;/code&gt;. This will ensure we are clearly attributed at the bottom of each post we write. Right now, this is clunky at best. I&amp;rsquo;m just using a static partial. If we want this to scale at some point, we&amp;rsquo;ll want to convert this to some sort of JSON object for each author.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;our-main-categories-will-be&#34;&gt;Our Main categories will be:&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Before and After&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Debugging&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Problem Solving&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide or How To&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opinion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;our-main-tags-will-be&#34;&gt;Our Main tags will be:&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Audio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Backend&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CSS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Code Example&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Front End&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Golang&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;HTML&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Javascript&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rails&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ruby&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Video&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sass&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Obviously we can add more to the categories and tags as needed. This is just a starting point. In the footer, you can see that each tag and category has it&amp;rsquo;s own landing page you can link to.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;here-s-how-to-add-a-quote-that-can-be-shared-on-twitter&#34;&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s how to add a quote that can be shared on Twitter&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Right now, we should limit this to one pullquote per post.&lt;/strong&gt; My js is looking for the first &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; on the page. I could refactor to loop through all blockquotes, but one seems sufficient.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=&#34; class=&#34;share-button&#34;&gt;Share on Twitter&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;


&lt;h2 id=&#34;images&#34;&gt;Images&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&amp;rsquo;re using Cloudinary again. In the front matter, save the directory and filename like this: &lt;code&gt;cloudinary = &amp;quot;v1479098109/workflow_ap2fh4.jpg&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&#34;inline-images&#34;&gt;Inline Images&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Created a shortcode &lt;code&gt;cloudinaryResponsiveImage&lt;/code&gt; for these guys. Pass a string just like above.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;image&#34;&gt;
  &lt;img
    data-src=&#39;https://res.cloudinary.com/dwjulenau/image/upload/c_fill,dpr_auto,q_auto,w_auto/v1464399447/screen-cap_calotu.jpg&#39;
    src=&#39;https://res.cloudinary.com/dwjulenau/image/upload/c_fill,dpr_auto,q_auto,w_auto/v1464399447/screen-cap_calotu.jpg&#39;
    alt=&#34;An image of sorts&#34;
    class=&#34;cld-responsive responsive-img&#34;
  &gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h2 id=&#34;adding-code-snippets&#34;&gt;Adding Code Snippets&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For code samples, we are using Pygments:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s an HTML Snippet:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34; data-lang=&#34;html&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;section&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;main&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;div&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;h1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;na&#34;&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;title&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;{{ .Title }}&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;h1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    {{ range .Data.Pages }}
      {{ .Render &amp;quot;summary&amp;quot;}}
    {{ end }}
  &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;div&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nt&#34;&gt;section&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s a Ruby Snippet:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-ruby&#34; data-lang=&#34;ruby&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;items&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;Mark&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;goobers&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;18&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;45&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;it&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;items&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;it&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;quot; &amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;print&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;se&#34;&gt;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s a Javascript Snippet:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-Javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;Javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;someVar&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;document&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;getElementsById&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s1&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;myVar&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;someVar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kd&#34;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;someVar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;++&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;someVar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nx&#34;&gt;innerHTML&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;quot;Some Thing&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h2 id=&#34;here-s-how-to-embed-a-tweet&#34;&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s how to embed a Tweet&lt;/h2&gt;

